entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You obliterated the mercenary recon team. They won't be reporting on you or anyone else ever again.
entries.journal_entry_description: Ordo has picked up a transmission from your area. He says it sounds like it's from some mercenaries that saw you messing with the AT-AT wreckage. It sounded like they were going to sell the information at the nearest Imperial base. He thinks it would be a good idea for you to make sure these mercs never reported to the Imperials what you were doing there.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Droma Ordo has contacted you about a transmission he picked up in your area. Check it out and make sure it's not a threat.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: The signal has stopped. I'm no longer receiving the transmission. I don't think they were able to contact their base. Good work.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Ordo is contacting you to let you know the signal had stopped.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Ordo to deliver the AT-AT information.
